#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gradle-tooling.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Native related properties can either be added in `application.properties` file, as command line arguments or in the `quarkusBuild` task.\n"
